===================================================================

Python Data Science Project .gitignore

===================================================================

--- Data Files ---

Ignore large data files. The user should be instructed in the README

on where to get the data and place it in the /data/ folder.

We are ignoring all CSV files inside the data folder.

/data/*.csv

--- Model Artifacts ---

Ignore trained models. These are generated by the training script

and should not be stored in version control.

/models/.joblib
/models/.pkl

--- Python Virtual Environments ---

Standard names for virtual environments. These contain installed

libraries and are specific to a local machine.

.env
.venv
env/
venv/
ENV/
env.bak/
venv.bak/

--- Python Cache & Compiled Files ---

These are temporary files generated by Python during execution.

pycache/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

--- IDE & Editor Folders ---

Configuration files for common editors.

.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

--- Jupyter Notebook ---

Ignore notebook checkpoints which are temporary backups.

.ipynb_checkpoints

--- Operating System Files ---

Common system-generated files (e.g., on macOS).

.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes

